<section class="help-card">
  <div class="help-card__eyebrow">Definition</div>
  <h2 class="help-card__title">
    What is {{ spaceType.label }} space?
  </h2>

  <p class="help-card__intro">
    {{ spaceType.label }} space in {{ city.city }} can vary widely by layout, size,
    building type, and lease structure. The right fit depends on how you plan to use
    the space day to day.
  </p>

  <div class="help-card__grid help-card__grid--tight">
    <div class="help-card__item">
      <h3>Typical use</h3>
      <p>
        {{ spaceType.label }} space supports a range of business needs depending on layout,
        location, and access.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="help-card__item">
      <h3>What varies most</h3>
      <p>
        Layout, visibility, parking, loading, ceiling height, frontage, and lease flexibility.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="help-card__item">
      <h3>Best way to start</h3>
      <p>
        Begin with size and use-case, then narrow by neighborhood, accessibility, and cost.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>